## Install pre-requisites

To start using Monitoring-as-Code, you also need to:

- [install Prometheus](https://prometheus.io/download/)
- [install Grafana](https://grafana.com/get/?plcmt=top-nav&cta=downloads)
- [install Docker](https://www.docker.com/get-started/)

## Test your installation
You can use the monitoring-grafana-journey-view mixin file to test that the product works as expected. The mixin file uses the Monitoring-as-Code product itself as an input to test.

